{
  "stem": "14251.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, everyone had heard about the Russians, the barbarians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we obviously had to hide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think there was one 15-year-old-- 14-year-old boy, her son, on hand, and that was the only reasonable male who could-- he's not going to be able to protect all these people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The day finally came-- or the week came that we finally had to go into the cellar and stay there, and we would stay there mostly during the night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the meantime, up the road from the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's not a street.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is just dirt, you know, dirt road, where the street was that's called in German, the chaussee.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chaussee is like a highway before there were highways-- the main street from one city to another, the connecting road, but a halfway decent road.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That road was filled with wall-to-wall people all trying to go westward, as they were told to do and were-- it was a law they had to obey.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, destroy everything you leave behind and move.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So the street was filled with that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And on some days, people would stop and ask for water, because they had walked for who knows how many cities away or villages away.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would try to give them what they could.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But by now disease was happening with these people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And by now the bombs had fallen even here and there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the water wasn't any good, had to boil that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In other words, we had to stop opening the door to strange people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we locked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And during the last week, we pretty much spent, I would say, 80% of the time in that cellar, because we could hear in the distance the Russian katyushas.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, those are the big guns.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
